snippet.title: Nobody's Left's official reveal trailer is finally out!
snippet.description:
This is only the beginning and we've got a long long road ahead of us. At this point we really need your support to help us keep going forward. You can do this simply by liking this video and sharing it with your friends.
Stay tuned, because the best is yet to come and we're going to release more details here on this channel. If you don't want to miss out on that, please consider subscribing.
Also, make sure to let us know what you think about Nobody's Left.

enjoy
